text: Kamyshly () is a rural locality (a village) in Bulgakovsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 758 as of 2010. There are 11 streets. == Geography == It is located 33 km from Ufa, 3 km from Bulgakovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Kamyshly, Ufimsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
